summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5783 for the improvement of East Highland Drive, from 24th Avenue North to 25th Avenue North; and a certain alley, by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 76256, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
